step_data.thought: The 'Export' button was clicked, but it doesn't seem to provide a direct option to generate a short link. The page now shows the export settings, which include bounding coordinates. However, there is no option to generate a short link here either. Given that the 'Share' button and the 'Export' button did not yield the desired result, I will now check if generating a short link is possible by navigating to a different page or if there is another method to accomplish this task. If not, I will inform the user that generating a short link is not currently supported on this page.
